  description_en = 'Vagabond Adventures are the premier English-speaking (& German, Czech, French et al!) provider of ski/snowboard lessons, ski holiday packages & off-piste guiding at Gudauri, Georgia. With their intimate local knowledge, they also organise fantastic ski safari tours throughout the country, combining resort, off-piste & snowcat skiing with the incredible Georgian culture.',
